OL,3,CManx performer reflects on
OL,4,C'devastating' teenage cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FA performer says her world 'just
OL,7,Fstopped' when she was diagnosed with
OL,8,Fcancer as a teenager, after being told
OL,9,Fshe had stage 2B Hodgkin lymphoma.
OL,11,FEvie Skillicorn, 20, spent most of
OL,12,F2025 in treatment and recovering from
OL,13,Fblood cancer, a condition most
OL,14,Fcommonly discovered in young people
OL,15,Fentering adulthood.
OL,17,FIn January, Evie was rehearsing for
OL,18,Fher starring role in the musical
OL,19,F'Chicago', after years of performing
OL,20,Fat the Gaiety Theatre in Douglas on
OL,21,Fthe Isle of Man.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
