PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777014326
OL,3,CManx performer reflects on
OL,4,C'devastating' teenage cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FFollowing multiple visits to the GP
OL,7,Fwith flu-like symptoms, she noticed a
OL,8,Flump on her throat, prompting a visit
OL,9,Fto the hospital.
OL,11,FAfter further scans at Noble's
OL,12,FHospital, she was then told it was
OL,13,Flymphoma.
OL,15,F"It was like a fever dream to be
OL,16,Fhonest," she said.
OL,18,F"And then when he said cancer, I think
OL,19,Fit's just like, your whole world just
OL,20,Fstops and so many things are rushing
OL,21,Fthrough your mind.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777014326
OL,3,CManx performer reflects on
OL,4,C'devastating' teenage cancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"I mean, the first thing that was
OL,7,Frushing through my mind was whether I
OL,8,Fcould do the show or not, which isn't
OL,9,Fgreat but it's devastating having your
OL,10,Fwhole life put on pause."
OL,12,FDespite her diagnosis, Evie was
OL,13,Fdetermined the show must go on, and
OL,14,Ftook to the stage each night, before
OL,15,Fher treatment began.
OL,17,FEvie then started her four-month
OL,18,Fchemotherapy treatment plan, where she
OL,19,Fbegan to lose her hair.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777014326
OL,3,CManx performer reflects on
OL,4,C'devastating' teenage cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FShe said: "I've always been quite a
OL,7,Fgirly person and felt quite feminine
OL,8,Fand I think losing your hair is a huge
OL,9,Fpoint of that femininity and your
OL,10,Fwhole identity.
OL,12,F"I'd already had so much taken from me
OL,13,Fand my identity as it is that I felt
OL,14,Fthis was just my final straw."
OL,16,FTo help cope with the treatment, Evie
OL,17,Fbegan to share her journey on TikTok.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
