PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777014326
OL,3,CManx performer reflects on
OL,4,C'devastating' teenage cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FAfter talking about her experience
OL,7,Fonline, she found new friends, and
OL,8,Frealised how many other people were
OL,9,Fexperiencing a similar diagnosis.
OL,11,F"I had so many lovely messages from
OL,12,Fpeople saying, 'hi I've had a similar
OL,13,Fdiagnosis, if there's anything you
OL,14,Fneed, let me know'.
OL,16,F"I made so many new friends through
OL,17,Fdifferent platforms of like speaking
OL,18,Fabout my diagnosis, and it felt really
OL,19,Fnice to try and help other people and
OL,20,Fspread awareness as well."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
