PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777014326
OL,3,CManx performer reflects on
OL,4,C'devastating' teenage cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FAfter finishing her treatment, Evie
OL,7,Fwas told the cancer had cleared - now
OL,8,Fawaiting the all clear in May.
OL,10,FReflecting on her treatment, Evie
OL,11,Fsaid: "I feel like I'm the same
OL,12,Fperson, but just a lot better version
OL,13,Fof myself.
OL,15,F"It shouldn't have had to take in
OL,16,Fsomething that traumatic to make me
OL,17,Finto this person, but I'm so glad that
OL,18,Fit did.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777014326
OL,3,CManx performer reflects on
OL,4,C'devastating' teenage cancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"And I think it kind of puts a lot of
OL,7,Fthings into perspective, and just not
OL,8,Fsacrificing my happiness for anything
OL,9,Fanymore has really helped get me on
OL,10,Ftrack and really helped my recovery
OL,11,Fprocess."
OL,13,FThe 20-year-old is now preparing to
OL,14,Fattend drama school in September,
OL,15,Fwhich she described as "incredibly
OL,16,Fexciting".
OL,18,F"I have always wanted to do drama as a
OL,19,Fcareer path. I don't care if that is
OL,20,Fjust singing, or just dancing, or just
OL,21,Facting, or musical theatre as a whole.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
